"{\"uid\": \"prnewswire.com-news-releases-three-stone-ridge-school-of-the-sacred-heart-graduates-and-top-athletes-compete-on-us-olympic-womens-swimming-team-302207254.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Searching for your content...  In-Language News  Contact Us  888-776-0942from 8 AM - 10 PM ET  Jul 25, 2024, 21:35 ET  Share this article  Gold MedalistKatie Ledecky('15) Joined byPhoebe Bacon('20)andErin Gemmell('23) in Paris Olympics 2024  BETHESDA, Md.,July 25, 2024/PRNewswire/ --Stone Ridge Schoolof the Sacred Heart, an all-girls 1-12 school inBethesda, Maryland, salutesKatie Ledecky\\u02bc15,Phoebe Bacon\\u02bc20, andErin Gemmell\\u02bc23 as they arrive inParisthis week to compete with TeamUSA.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"score\": 0.9967486641644118, \"rank\": 0.0029393923166348896, \"text\": \"Maryland\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Representing 15% of the 2024 U.S. Olympic Women's Swimming Team, all three renowned Stone Ridge \\\"Gators\\\" graduated from the independent all-girls school inBethesda, Maryland.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"score\": 0.9967486641644118, \"rank\": 0.0029393923166348896, \"text\": \"Maryland\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maryland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While not uncommon for swimmers from the same college to be named to an Olympic Team together, it is nearly unheard of for three athletes from the same high school to achieve this feat.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We at Stone Ridge are incredibly proud of these athletes, not only for what they accomplish in the sport of swimming, but for the values and character they represent,\\\" said Head of SchoolCatherine Ronan Karrels'86.\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our school community has watched these young women train for many years, consistently inspired by their dedication to hitting their goals in the pool while achieving high standards in their academics and other pursuits.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While swimmers strive for their personal best, each one of these champion athletes is also fully dedicated to the concept of team and community - a true lesson on the payoff of consistent hard work, discipline, and practice.\\\"\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stone Ridge Schoolof the Sacred Heart endeavors to develop empowered leaders who serve with faith, intellect, and confidence.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1513, \"end\": 1524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"score\": 0.9429892133255964, \"rank\": 0.05718954248365827, \"text\": \"Stone Ridge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\"}, {\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"score\": 0.9997588080199442, \"rank\": 0.00024055597557289543, \"text\": \"Sacred Heart\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The school is part of a 200-year-old international network of Sacred Heart schools sponsored by the Religious of the Sacred Heart, with origins inFrance.\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"score\": 0.9997588080199442, \"rank\": 0.00024055597557289543, \"text\": \"Sacred Heart\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Society_of_the_Sacred_Heart\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Students learn to tackle challenges and develop leadership skills while maintaining a healthy balance in their lives-an ideal blend of support and challenge for young athletes.\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The new level of inspiration and motivation brought by Ledecky's record-breaking career has also contributed to the increase in elite-level athletes graduating from Stone Ridge in the twelve years since her Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2136, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"score\": 0.9429783719058429, \"rank\": 0.05718954248365827, \"text\": \"Stone Ridge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Erin and Phoebe have told us they were both deeply inspired by Katie when they were younger, and the spirit of sisterhood they demonstrate is part of our school culture,\\\" Karrels continued.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\", \"score\": 0.9999822170319508, \"rank\": 1.360640029764887e-05, \"text\": \"Erin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erin_Hannon\"}, {\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\", \"score\": 0.79823347902615, \"rank\": 0.25276244033678846, \"text\": \"Phoebe\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoebe_Halliwell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My heart is bursting with pride in these young women, and I feel incredibly grateful to be inspired by them and learn from their dedication and grit.\\\"\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Karrels is traveling toParisthis week to cheer on her former students.\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hundreds of members of the Stone Ridge community gathered on campus the evening before the Opening Ceremony to cheer on the Olympians.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"score\": 0.9429783719058429, \"rank\": 0.05718954248365827, \"text\": \"Stone Ridge\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stone_Ridge,_New_York\"}, {\"begin\": 2700, \"end\": 2716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9792077061663192, \"rank\": 0.01786987116442162, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics_opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AboutStone Ridge Schoolof the Sacred HeartStone Ridge Schoolof the Sacred Heart, located inBethesda, Maryland, is an all-girls grades 1-12, Catholic, independent school with a coeducational program for children ages three months through Kindergarten.\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [{\"b